# 3. Framework Application Process

This section presents the application process of the UPICEF framework in real-world contexts.
It explains how the framework should be applied, by whom, in which situations, and for what purpose.

The focus of this section is the operationalization of UPICEF as a diagnostic tool for assessing
the structural completeness of urban planning instruments.

---

## Purpose

The purpose of the Framework Application Process is to provide a clear, replicable, and transparent
method for applying UPICEF to planning documents, independently of their policy content.

---

## Contents

- Framework application workflow
- Description of application activities
- Inputs and outputs of each activity
- Target audience and usage scenarios

